34.5%、“75后”占39.9%、“85后”占49.3%，在职场中的“存在感”均比Z世代更强。在困扰Z世代的职场问题中，“工作强度太大，工作量与收入不成正比”排在第2位。在职场上，Z世代渴望在情感上得到平等对待，实现付出与收入的平衡。仅3成95后每天工作超过9小时，Z世代不如前辈“肯吃苦”？"},"attached_info":"CkAI9ufNtMSamb00EAMaCDcwNTgwODkzIOLSj4oGMM0BOO4ZQANyCTQ4NzM0NTgzOHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"515 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-15eb043a102fa581320d75852dcc25f8_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"4_1631930048.652703","card_id":"Q_446705543","target":{"id":446705543,"title":"为什么会有「爬完泰山会分手」的说法？为什么会把分手归因于爬泰山，是出于什么心理？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/446705543","type":"question","created":1614419794,"answer_count":1131,"follower_count":3455,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[2506,4729,4758,7321,9628],"comment_count":99,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"在网上看到很多文案都说爬完泰山会分手。有些想不通。"},"attached_info":"Cj8I9ufNtMSamb00EAMaCDYxNTQ2NDA0INKu6IEGMGM4/xpABHIJNDQ2NzA1NTQzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"430 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-aae6100d1a8851170dba054c7d185d0f_720w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"5_1631930048.6531038","card_id":"Q_487396480","target":{"id":487396480,"title":"新娘自称「有病」婚礼现场跪求悔婚，男方同意悔婚后女方拒绝退还 30 多万彩礼和礼金，哪些信息值得关注？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/487396480","type":"question","created":1631852265,"answer_count":994,"follower_count":3314,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[982,3510,5582,9571,99628],"comment_count":211,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"“我对不起你们，你给你儿子找个好的吧“结婚当天，新娘跪地磕头要悔婚！回想起2020年6月10日花30多万给儿子举办的婚礼，商丘卢女士的心里就难受不已，她怎么也没想到，刚过门的儿媳妇竟在婚礼现场，当着宾客的面自称”有病“跪求他们要悔婚。既然不想结婚，女方为何不提前向男方表明态度